mili is a 1975 bollywood romantic drama film directed by hrishikesh mukherjee .   it starred amitabh bachchan , jaya bachchan and ashok kumar in lead roles .   jaya bachchan received a filmfare nomination as best actress , the only nomination for the film .   the film was later remade in telugu in 1976 as jyothi starring jayasudha in the title role .